====== H7378: רִיב ======

===== Source =====

or   ; a primitive root;

===== Meaning =====

properly, to  toss , i.e.  grapple ; mostly figuratively, to  wrangle , i.e.  hold a controversy ; (by implication) to  defend

===== Definitions =====

  - toss
  - grapple
  - wrangle
  - hold a controversy
  - defend

===== Usage =====

adversary, chide, complain, contend, debate, × ever, × lay wait, plead, rebuke, strive, × thoroughly.
